snippet.title: Live Coding: Mobile App w/ React Native (GPS bookmarker)
snippet.description:
Let's build on top of the React knowledge we learned last night. Let's build an Android app! (will work on iOS too). We build a Bitcoin price checker and an app that allows us to bookmark GPS locations! We also learn how to package the APK file for distribution to other Android users.

GitHub: https://www.github.com/DevDungeon
Support the stream: https://streamlabs.com/devdungeon
Join Discord: https://discord.gg/JWsSHJC
Get $100 credit for signing up to Digital Ocean: https://m.do.co/c/5ccd98162d85 
Buy my book: Security with Go https://www.packtpub.com/networking-and-servers/security-go

YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/DevDungeon
